---
title: African-Inspired Beyond Meat® and Peanut Soup with Kidney Beans and Sesame Flatbreads
description: Rich peanut butter, Beyond Meat® and fibre-loaded kidney beans make for a creamy and oh-so-filling soup! The golden sesame seed flatbreads are perfect for dipping, too! This one's a keeper for those days when you want to go veggie without compromising on protein.
